msgid "Episode I: Escape the Living"
msgstr "エピソード I: 生の逃走"

#. [campaign]
#: The_Dark_Hordes/_main.cfg:66
msgid ""
"This is the tale of an age when the glory of Wesnoth was being transformed "
"into arrogance. The fugitive necromancer Gwiti Ha’atel is resolved to master "
"the undead hordes and exact his revenge against all who have betrayed him. "
"His journey eventually leaves his own hands, morphing into an enormous wave "
"of power...\n"
"\n"
"(Intermediate level, 8 scenarios.)"
msgstr ""
"これは Wesnoth の栄光が傲慢へと姿を変えつつあった時代の物語。逃走したネクロマ"
"ンサー Gwiti Ha’atel は、アンデッドの大軍団を支配し、彼を裏切った全ての人々へ"
"復讐を果たす事を決意した。彼の旅はやがて彼自身の手を離れ、巨大な力の波へと変"
"貌を遂げる......\n"
"\n"
"（中級レベル、8 シナリオ）"

