#. [campaign]
#: The_Dark_Hordes/_main.cfg:82
msgid "Episode II: The Death March"
msgstr "エピソード II: 死の行軍"

#. [campaign]
#: The_Dark_Hordes/_main.cfg:82
msgid ""
"At last, the deadly forces brought by Gwiti launched their invasion against "
"Wesnoth. As the shadows of his rule terrorize the Kingdom and its people, "
"they turn to the elven enchantress Elynia for their last breath of hope. "
"Will the Light or the Darkness be the one that stands in the end? There was "
"no one who knew, except only one.\n"
"\n"
"(Intermediate level, 6 scenarios.)"
msgstr ""
"遂に Gwiti の死の力が Wesnoth に対する侵略を開始した。彼の支配する影が王国と"
"その人々を恐怖に陥れる中、彼らは最後の望みをエルフの魔法使い Elynia に託す。"
"最後に立っているのは光か、それとも闇なのか？知る者はただ一人を除いて存在しな"
"かった。\n"
"\n"
"（中級レベル、6 シナリオ）"

