#. [unit]: type=Ogre, id=Rek Iceheart
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:109
msgid "Rek Iceheart"
msgstr "Rek Iceheart"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:131
msgid "Ugh... Am I still breathing? My body still aches..."
msgstr "うぐっ... 私は... まだ息をしているのか？まだ体中が痛む..."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:135
msgid ""
"Gwiti gradually accepted that he had reached some strange beach. The area "
"was quiet but the beastly smell had stayed."
msgstr ""
"Gwiti は徐々に、自分が見知らぬ海岸へ辿り着いた事を受け入れた。辺りは静まり"
"返っていたが、獣の臭いが漂っていた。"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:152
msgid ""
"My shackles are broken. I think, disgustingly, I know that the contrivance "
"of destiny is always ironic... Yet why is there no Nati by my side? Where "
"has he gone?"
msgstr ""
"私の束縛は解けた。運命の企みはいつも皮肉だ、嫌になる程に... しかし私の隣に "
"Nati がいないのは何故だ？彼はどこへ行ったのだ？"

#. [message]: speaker=Xabrak
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:175
msgid ""
"Hey! Look over there! A feeble necromancer is approaching us! But strange... "
"I thought all the cults in this land were vanquished by us."
msgstr ""
"おい！あの場所を見ろ！弱々しい黒魔術師が接近している！しかし奇妙だ... この土"
"地の教団は、全て我々が駆逐したと思っていたのに。"

#. [message]: speaker=Grakarat
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:179
msgid ""
"I hate humans! I hate skeletons! But I love the feel of crushing their bones."
msgstr "人間は嫌い！骸骨も嫌い！でも奴らの骨を砕く感触は大好き。"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:201
msgid ""
"... Now it seems I must abandon any consideration and survive from their "
"aggression. Fortunately or unfortunately, there are many bodies left among "
"the ruin that I may evoke. But after I summon them, the time I have left may "
"not be so long."
msgstr ""
"...... 今は、私は考える事を捨て、奴らの攻撃から生き延びなければならない。幸か"
"不幸か、この廃墟には私が呼び起こす事のできる多くの亡骸が残っている。だが彼ら"
"を召還した後、私に残された時間はそう長くないかもしれない。"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:212
msgid "Our plunder ends... by the darkness..."
msgstr "略奪が、俺達の略奪が終わる... 闇によって..."

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:222
msgid "Who is hidden there? I wish you are on my side, though."
msgstr "そこに隠れているのは誰だ？私の側にあって欲しいのだが。"

#. [unit]: id=Arkal-Thil, type=Dark Adept
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:228
msgid "Arkal-Thil"
msgstr "Arkal-Thil"

#. [message]: speaker=Arkal-Thil
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:247
msgid "I almost got murdered by them..."
msgstr "奴らに殺される手前だった......"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:252
msgid ""
"Who the hell are you? My guess is that you are the necromancer... right?"
msgstr "お前は一体何者だ？私の予想では、お前はネクロマンサーだ... 違うか？"

#. [message]: speaker=Arkal-Thil
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:257
msgid ""
"Exactly. I am the same kind of person as you. I was one of the followers of "
"the darkness who trained in this land. But those beasts came and slayed our "
"master, and destroyed many of us."
msgstr ""
"確かに、そして私はあなたと同じ種類の人間です。私はこの土地で行を重ねる闇の信"
"奉者の一人でした。しかしあの獣共がやって来て、我らの師を殺し、我らの多くを滅"
"ぼしたのです。"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:261
msgid "So, you want your new master? Then you should join my... uprising."
msgstr ""
"そして、お前は新しい師を求めている、と？ならば加わるべきだ... 私の蜂起へ。"

#. [message]: speaker=Arkal-Thil
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:265
msgid "Uprising? For what?"
msgstr "蜂起？何の為に？"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:269
msgid ""
"It would be easier to understand if I say that it is revenge against all the "
"corrupt living? You and other survivors of yours have all been oppressed by "
"the mighty... right? I need that kind of anger, that kind of grief."
msgstr ""
"腐った、生きている全ての連中への復讐、と言えば分かりやすいかな？お前やお前の"
"他の生存者達は、全て強大な存在によって虐げられた... 違うか？私はその怒り、そ"
"の悲愴を求めている。"

#. [message]: speaker=Arkal-Thil
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:273
msgid ""
"It is quite an interesting irony that you remind me of our past. No? In any "
"case, there is no reason to refuse. We will follow you. But in fact, there "
"must be another one who is being held hostage by the ogre."
msgstr ""
"私に我々の過去を思い出させるとは、面白い皮肉ですね。違いますか？いずれにせ"
"よ、拒否する理由はありません。我々はあなたに従います。しかし実の所、もう一"
"人、オーガの人質となっている者がいるのですが。"

#. [objective]: condition=lose
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:288
msgid "Death of Arkal-Thil"
msgstr "Arkal-Thil の死"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:312
msgid "Argh! I was vanquished!"
msgstr "あぐっ！俺... 敗れた。"

