#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:407
msgid "I perish here and now... Even though I have made my escape."
msgstr "私はここで、今滅ぶ... 脱出したばかりにも関わらず。"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:420
msgid "I feel the shadows drawing me closer..."
msgstr "ああ、影が私を呼び寄せて..."

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:430
msgid ""
"Apparently the Wesnothians noticed my escape and sent reinforcements here. "
"All my luck has run out..."
msgstr ""
"Wesnoth 人が私の脱出に気付き、援軍をここへ派遣したらしい。私の運は全て尽き"
"た..."

